[MessageBox]
ExitGame_Title=Exit
ExitGame_Message=Are you sure you want to exit the game?
LogOut_Title=Logout
LogOut_Message=Are you sure you want to logout?
StartGame_Title=Start Match?
StartGame_Message=Start the match using the current settings?
StartDedicated_Title=Start Dedicated Server?
StartDedicated_Message=Start a dedicated server using the current settings?
FirstTimeCharacter_Title=Create Character
FirstTimeCharacter_Message=It looks like you have not yet customized your online character.  Would you like to do that now?  If not, a character will be randomly generated for you.
MustLogoutToLogin_Title=Must Logout
MustLogoutToLogin_Message=In order to login to a new profile, you must logout of your currently logged-in profile.  Would you like to logout now?
ProfileCreated_Title=Profile Created
ProfileCreated_Message=Your profile has been created.  You can now login with the user name specified.
BindKey_Title=Bind Key
BindKey_Message=Press the key or button you wish to bind to.\nThe key will be bound to '`Binding`'\n(Shift-Escape Cancels)
ResetToPreset_Title=Reset to Preset
ResetToPreset_Message=By returning to preset mode, your customized controls will be lost.  Are you sure you want to do this?
ResetToDefaults_Title=Reset to Defaults
ResetToDefaults_Message=By resetting to defaults, your customized settings will be lost.  Are you sure you want to do this?
FriendRequestSent_Title=Friend Request Sent
FriendRequestSent_Message=Your friend request was sent to '`PlayerName`'.
FriendRequestFailed_Title=Error
FriendRequestFailed_Message=Failed to send a friend request to '`PlayerName`', please try again later.
RemoveFriend_Title=Remove Friend
RemoveFriend_Message=Are you sure you want to remove '`PlayerName`' from your friends list?
SentGameInvite_Title=Sent Game Invite
SentGameInvite_Message=An invite to play Unreal Tournament 3 has been sent to '`PlayerName`'!
JoinFriend_Message=Joining...
ViewMessage_Title=View Message
ViewMessage_Message=Message From '`PlayerName`':\n\n`Message`
ViewFriendRequest_Title=Accept Friend Request
ViewFriendRequest_Message=Friend request from '`PlayerName`':\n\n`Message`
ViewGameInvite_Title=Accept Game Invite
ViewGameInvite_Message=Game invite from '`PlayerName`':\n\n`Message`
DeleteMessage_Title=Delete Message
DeleteMessage_Message=Delete message from '`PlayerName`'?
DeleteContent_Title=Delete Content
DeleteContent_Message=Delete the `ContentName` content package?  This action is not reversible!
DeleteAllContent_Title=Delete All
DeleteAllContent_Message=Delete all content packages?  This action is not reversible!
ImportingMod_Message=Importing Mod...
UnpackingMod_Message=Unpacking Mod...
InstallPS3Start_Message=Installing...
InstallPS3Cancelling_Message=Cancelling Install...
InstallPS3Progress_Message=Installing... (`CurrentFile` of `TotalFiles`)
InstallPS3Finished_Title=Install Complete
InstallPS3Finished_Message=Unreal Tournament 3 has been fully installed.
KeepResolution_Title=Keep Settings?
KeepResolution_Message=Your resolution has been changed.  Do you want to keep these new settings?\n(Will automatically revert in `Seconds` second(s))
DownloadContent_Title=Download Content
DownloadContent_Message=The game will minimize and a webbrowser will launch to finish your content download.  Would you like to continue?
SavingProfile=Saving Game. Please do not turn off the PLAYSTATIONｮ3 system.
EnterUnlockCode_Title=Unlock Character
EnterUnlockCode_Message=Enter character unlock code:
EnterServerPassword_Title=Password Required
EnterServerPassword_Message=This server requires a password to join.  Please enter the correct password to continue.
FirstTimeMultiplayer_Title=Setup Settings
FirstTimeMultiplayer_Message=You must set your player name and internet settings before entering multiplayer.
StompBindKey_Title=Duplicate Binding
StompBindKey_Message=This action binds a command to a key that is already bound. Do you want to remove the previous binding?
CrucialBindErrorMsg=A crucial action is not bound to input.  Please bind the action to continue.
LoseChangesWarning_Title=Lose unsaved changes
LoseChangesWarning_Message=You are about to lose unsaved changes.  Would you like to continue?
QueryPending_Message=Please wait while the active query is completed.
EnterServerIP_Title=Join IP
EnterServerIP_Message=Enter the IP address and Port (in the format IP:Port) of the server you wish to join.
AddServerIP_Title=Add IP
AddServerIP_Message=Enter the IP address and Port (in the format IP:Port) of the server you wish to add.
FindServerIPFail_Title=Error
FindServerIPFail_Message=Failed to find a server matching the specified IP and Port.
FindServerIPFailConnect_Message=Do you wish to connect directly instead?
FindServerIPUninitialized_Message=Failed to initialize the query handler.
FindServerIPInProgress_Message=Failed to initialize the query handler, as a query is already in progress.
FindServerIPNotLoggedIn_Message=Failed to start query, not logged in.
FindServerIPInvalid_Message=Invalid IP address.
FindServerIPInvalidResult_Message=Invalid query result.
FindServerIPJoinFailed_Message=Failed to join the server matching the specified IP and Port.
AddIPAlreadyPresent_Message=Server already in favorites.
SteamFail_License=Sorry, you do not appear to be authorized to play this game on Steam at this time.
SteamFail_Connection=Unable to authenticate with Steam. Check your Steam connection.
SteamFail_Cheat=You have been marked as a cheater by Steam.
SteamFail_Generic=Unable to authenticate with Steam; reason unknown.


[Errors]
Error_Title=Error
JoinGameFailed_Title=Error
JoinGameFailed_Message=Unable to join the selected match.  Please try another match.
QuickMatchFailed_Title=Error
QuickMatchFailed_Message=Unable to find a suitable match for quick play.  Please try revising your filter settings and try again.
IncompatibleVersion_Title=Error
IncompatibleVersion_Message=The match you are trying to join is running an incompatible version of the game.  Please try upgrading your game version.
UnableToFindMatch_Title=Error
UnableToFindMatch_Message=Unable to find a match with the filters you described.  Please try changing your filters and searching again.
LoginRequired_Title=Error
LoginRequired_Message=This feature requires a currently logged in profile to continue.
GoldRequired_Title=Error
GoldRequired_Message=This feature requires a Xbox Live Gold membership to continue.
OnlineRequired_Title=Error
OnlineRequired_Message=Your profile does not allow online play.  Access to online features will be disabled.
ContentRequired_Title=Error
ContentRequired_Message=Your profile does not allow user created content.  Access to custom content features will be disabled.
CommunicationRequired_Title=Error
CommunicationRequired_Message=Your profile does not allow online communication.  Access to communication features will be disabled.
OnlineRequiredForInternet_Message=Certain features require an online profile.  Access to online features will be disabled.
LinkDisconnected_Message=No network connection detected.  Please check to make sure you are connected to a network to continue.
NetworkLinkLost_Message=You no longer have a valid network connection.  Please double-check your network cables and configuration.
ConnectionLost_Title=Error
ConnectionLost_Message=Your connection to the server was lost.
InvalidMessage_Title=Error
InvalidMessage_Message=The message you have entered is blank.  Please enter a longer message.
InvalidUserName_Title=Error
InvalidUserName_Message=The user name you have entered is invalid.  A valid user name and password must be entered to login.
InvalidUserName_LocalLogin=You must enter a name for your local profile.  Password is not required.
InvalidUserNameCreateProfile_Message=The user name you have entered is invalid.  User names must be between 3 and 15 characters.
InvalidUserNameFirstChar_Message=The user name you have entered is invalid.  A user name cannot start with a number, a space, or any of the following characters: #, @, +
InvalidCDKey_Title=Error
InvalidCDKey_Message=The CD key you have entered is invalid.  A valid CD Key is required to continue.  Please check your entry and try again.
InvalidFriendName_Title=Error
InvalidFriendName_Message=The friend name you have entered is invalid.  Please double check the spelling of your friend's name.
InvalidPassword_Title=Error
InvalidPassword_Message=The password you have entered has an invalid length.  A valid user name and password must be entered to login.
InvalidPasswordConfirm_Title=Error
InvalidPasswordConfirm_Message=The password and the password confirmation you have entered do not match.
InvalidPasswordForEmail_Title=Error
InvalidPasswordForEmail_Message=The password provided is invalid for the existing account based on the specified email address. If you have forgotten your username or password, please visit http://www.gamespyid.com.
InvalidEMail_Title=Error
InvalidEMail_Message=The email address you have entered is invalid.
NameInUse_Title=Error
NameInUse_Message=The user name you have provided is already in-use.  Please choose a different user name.
ServiceUnavailable_Title=Error
ServiceUnavailable_Message=The online service is currently unavailable.  Please wait and try reconnecting again.
UpdateRequired_Title=Error
UpdateRequired_Message=To continue playing online, you must update your software version.
ServersTooBusy_Title=Error
ServersTooBusy_Message=The online servers are currently too busy.  Please wait and try reconnecting again.
DuplicateLogin_Title=Error
DuplicateLogin_Message=A duplicate login has been detected.  Your connection to the server has been lost.
InvalidUserLogin_Title=Error
InvalidUserLogin_Message=The username and password provided are invalid.  Please check the spelling of your username and password.  Passwords are case sensitive. If you have forgotten your username or password, please visit http://www.gamespyid.com.
LogoutFailed_Title=Error
LogoutFailed_Message=Logout Failed
ProfileCreationFailed_Title=Error
ProfileCreationFailed_Message=Profile creation failed.  The User Name cannot contain any blank spaces or start with a non-alphanumeric character. Please try creating your profile again.
FailedToSendMessage_Title=Error
FailedToSendMessage_Message=Failed to send message to '`PlayerName`', please try again later.
JoinFriendFailed_Title=Error
JoinFriendFailed_Message=Failed to join your friend's game.  The game may already be full.
SendInviteFailed_Title=Invite to Game Failed
SendInviteFailed_Message=Failed to invite '`PlayerName`' to your game.
CampaignOnlineFailure_Title=Alert
CampaignOnlineFailure=Internet play has been disabled. Please enable your profile if you wish to play online with others.
FailedToReadNews=There was an error reading the latest news from the online news server.  Please try again later.
FailedToReadContent=There was an error reading the latest content from the online content server.  Please try again later.
EmptyMapCycle_Title=Error
EmptyMapCycle_Message=You need to add at least one map to your map cycle to begin the match.
SomeChangesMayNotBeApplied_Title=Warning
SomeChangesMayNotBeApplied_Message=Some changes may not be applied until the game is restarted.
NeedSecondController_Title=Error
NeedSecondController_Message=There needs to be 2 controllers connected before beginning a splitscreen match.
CannotSendFriendRequestToYourself_Title=Error
CannotSendFriendRequestToYourself_Message=You are unable to add yourself as a friend.  Please enter another username to send the request to.
CannotSendMessageToYourself_Title=Error
CannotSendMessageToYourself_Message=You are unable to send yourself messages.  Please enter another username to send the message to.
CannotUseKeyboardMouse_Title=Error
CannotUseKeyboardMouse_Message=Using the keyboard and/or mouse is prohibited on this server.
CanOnlyConfigureEnabledMutators_Title=Error
CanOnlyConfigureEnabledMutators_Message=Only enabled mutators can be configured.
CurrentMutatorCannotBeConfigured_Title=Error
CurrentMutatorCannotBeConfigured_Message=The currently selected mutator is not configurable.
InvalidUnlockCode_Title=Error
InvalidUnlockCode_Message=The unlock code you have entered is incorrect.  Please check your spelling and try again.
NotAllPlayersCanJoin_Title=Error
NotAllPlayersCanJoin_Message=Not all local players have permission to join the game invite.
NotEnoughInviteSpace_Title=Error
NotEnoughInviteSpace_Message=Not enough space for all local players in the game invite.
UnableToJoinInvite_Title=Error
UnableToJoinInvite_Message=Unable to join the game invite.  The game may already be full.
StrictNAT_Message=Your network configuration may not be compatible with hosting matches.  Please check your router's manual for instructions on setting up 'Port Forwarding' or a 'DMZ server'.
MinSpecMessage=Your machine is being detected as below the minimum system requirements for Unreal Tournament 3. Please check the Release Notes for suggestions on improving your visual quality.

